sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant N as NeoServlet
    participant A as JWT Auth
    participant S as ETGO_SF_* Tables
    participant F as NeoFieldFilter
    participant H as NeoHandler (CDI)
    participant D as DataSourceServlet

    C->>N: HTTP Request /sws/neo/{spec}/{entity}
    N->>A: Validate token
    A-->>N: User context

    N->>S: Lookup ETGO_SF_SPEC + ENTITY
    S-->>N: Spec config + entity config

    N->>F: Build filter from ETGO_SF_FIELD

    alt POST / PUT / PATCH (Write)
        F->>F: Strip non-included & read-only fields from request body
    end

    alt CDI Hook configured
        N->>H: handle(NeoContext)
        alt Hook returns response
            H-->>N: NeoResponse
        else Hook returns null
            H-->>N: null (fallthrough)
            N->>D: Forward to DataSourceServlet
            D-->>N: JSON response
        end
    else No hook
        N->>D: Forward to DataSourceServlet
        D-->>N: JSON response
    end

    alt GET (Read)
        F->>F: Strip non-included fields from response
    end

    N-->>C: Filtered JSON response
